Signed-off-by: Mingcong Bai <jeffbai@aosc.io>
---
 drivers/iommu/intel/iommu.c | 1 +
 1 file changed, 1 insertion(+)

diff --git a/drivers/iommu/intel/iommu.c b/drivers/iommu/intel/iommu.c
